### Audio – unknown callType (expect 202 + warning in func log)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/audio
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary={{boundary}}

--{{boundary}}
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="metadata"
Content-Type: application/json

{"callType":"UNKNOWN|CODE","caseId":"TEST-004","phone":"5550000000","timestamp":"1745000003000","brandId":"4600"}
--{{boundary}}
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="test.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ../TestData/test.wav
--{{boundary}}--


### Audio – missing caseId (expect 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/audio
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary={{boundary}}

--{{boundary}}
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="metadata"
Content-Type: application/json

{"callType":"D|FR","phone":"9794920458","timestamp":"1745000004000","brandId":"4600"}
--{{boundary}}
