# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# 2. POST /api/image
#    Needs Pipeline:EnableTranscription=true + real transcription URL
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Image – (enable transcription in local.settings.json first)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/image
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary={{boundary}}

--{{boundary}}
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="invoice.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ../TestData/test.wav
--{{boundary}}--
